_sText:
So this is a revision of surf_akai_final. Working on surf_akai_2 got me thinking I should fix some things in the first one. The jail has received a 60% change, hopefully for the better, camping should be almost eliminated now. I added several more secrets around the map. I hope this can be the version you all originally wanted, and I apologize for not getting surf_akai_2 to you all sooner, but it should be done soon.
